snippet.title: Phun - 2D physics sandbox
snippet.description:
Phun goes Algodoo! Download a free trial of Algodoo at: http://www.algodoo.com

Phun was created as a MSc project by Emil Ernerfeldt for supervisor Kenneth Bodin, HPC2N/VRlab, Umeå University, Sweden.

On popular demand, here is the music (which I also wrote):
http://www.phunland.com/download/Phun_theme.mp3
Copyright Emil Ernerfeldt
